      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable, Well-Maintained & Ready to Hit the Road \u2014 A Smart Everyday Choice! This solid used car is in good condition and has been thoughtfully cared for over the years. The exterior shows the expected light wear and minor surface scuffs you'd find on a well-used vehicle, while the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs reliably and is ready for your daily commute or weekend adventures. If you're looking for a trustworthy ride at a fair price, this one checks all the boxes!",
