    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in exceptional, mint condition and represents a rare find in the used car market. The car shows virtually no signs of wear; the exterior finish is clean and vibrant with no notable scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the interior is immaculate with fresh, well-maintained upholstery and surfaces throughout. Mechanically, the vehicle performs flawlessly \u2014 all systems, electronics, and components are in excellent working order, and it drives as smoothly and responsively as one would expect from a nearly new vehicle. This is an outstanding opportunity for a buyer seeking a used car that truly looks and feels like it just came off the lot.",
