      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a bare-bones budget option? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it's had a tough life and it shows! The exterior has visible dents, scratches, and wear throughout, and the interior is well-used. Mechanically, this car will need attention before it's road-ready. That said, it could be a rewarding project for the right hands, or a solid source of parts. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, at an honest price!",
      "price": 5500.0,
