    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $5,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor overall condition. Buyers should be fully aware of what they're getting: the exterior shows significant wear, including multiple scratches, chips, dents, and faded paint in several areas. The interior has notable wear and tear \u2014 upholstery is worn or torn in spots, and trim pieces show their age. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention; it runs but is not in reliable day-to-day condition without repairs. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer comfortable investing in repairs after purchase. No attempt has been made to hide or minimize the car's shortcomings \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that reality.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you will find on the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains a deep, showroom-quality shine and bodywork completely free of dents, scratches, or blemishes. The interior is equally impressive: all surfaces are pristine, the upholstery shows no wear, and every button, knob, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, effortless power, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, cooling, and electrical \u2014 are in outstanding working order. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires absolutely nothing before hitting the road; no deferred maintenance, no hidden surprises. Ideal for a discerning buyer who demands the very best in a pre-owned vehicle. Priced at $46,500, reflecting its outstanding condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
